      "content": "im not sure if i want to go to the er, the wait times are always so bad and it's so expensive. do u really think it's a panic attack? it just feels so heavy. if i take the med and it works, can i just stay home and sleep it off? i don't want to make a big deal out of nothing if its just my anxiety acting up again.",
