      "content": "it's just so hard to tell the difference. i'm sitting here and it's just that heavy pressure. if it was a heart thing, wouldn't i be having more sharp pain or something? i feel like i'm just overthinking it because of my anxiety. honestly if i just take a double dose of my meds right now, would that be enough to make sure it's just a panic attack and i can just sleep? i'd rather just sleep it off than deal with a hospital if i can help it.",
